.TH TP-LINT 1 "February 2026" "tp-lint 1.5.2" "User Commands"
.SH NÁZOV
tp-lint \- Translation Project linter and statistics tool
.SH PREHĽAD
.B tp-lint
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fILANG\fR]
.SH POPIS
.B tp-lint
checks translation status against the GNU Translation Project matrix.
Shows coverage statistics and generates reports for translation teams.
.SH MOŽNOSTI
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version number and exit.
.TP
.BR \-\-stats " " [\fILANG\fR]
Show translation statistics. Without LANG shows global stats.
.TP
.BR \-\-domain " " \fIPKG\fR
Show statistics for specific package/domain.
.TP
.BR \-\-top " " \fIN\fR
Number of items in top/bottom lists (default: 10).
.TP
.BR \-\-report " " [\fILANG\fR]
Generate translation status report.
.TP
.BR \-\-report\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Report format: markdown (default), html
.TP
.BR \-\-report\-output " " \fIFILE\fR
Save report to file instead of stdout.
.TP
.BR \-\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format: text (default), json
.TP
.BR \-\-refresh
Force refresh of cached TP matrix data.
.SH NÁVRATOVÝ KÓD
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
Error occurred.
.SH PRÍKLADY
.TP
Show global translation statistics:
.B tp-lint \-\-stats
.TP
Show statistics for Swedish:
.B tp-lint \-\-stats sv
.TP
Generate HTML report for German:
.B tp-lint \-\-report de \-\-report\-format html \-\-report\-output de.html
.TP
Check specific package:
.B tp-lint \-\-domain coreutils
